    <h1>Company</h1>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container">
  <div class="info-container bg-white">
    <div class="content-card">
      <div class="card-text-area">
        <div class="card-text">
          <h3>What we do</h3>
          <p>CF PharmTech was founded in Wuxi, Jiangsu province in 2008. Through rapid growth, it becomes a fully integrated specialty pharmaceutical company dedicated to providing high-quality respiratory drugs for the global market.  Managed by a high-caliber team with extensive experience in the industry, the company focuses on the development of drugs for the treatment of respiratory diseases in its state-of-the-art facilities.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-img-area">
        <img class="card-img" src="<%= asset_path 'about-us-1.jpg' %>" alt="">
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="Our-Mission" class="content-card">
      <div class="card-text-area">
        <div class="card-text">
          <h3>Mission</h3>
          <p>Our mission is to develop high-quality and affordable products to treat respiratory diseases and help patients to breathe easier and live better.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-img-area">
        <img class="card-img" src="<%= asset_path 'about-us-2.jpg' %>" alt="">
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="Our-Values" class="content-card">
      <div class="card-img-area">
        <img class="card-img" src="<%= asset_path 'about-us-3.jpg' %>" alt="">
      </div>
      <div class="card-text-area">
        <div class="card-text">
          <h3>Values</h3>
          <p>Our values are integrity, patient-focus, science-led innovation.</p>
          <p>Integrity</p>
          <p>Patient Focus</p>
          <p>Science-led Innovation</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="History" class="content-card">
      <div class="card-text-area background-grey">
        <div class="card-text">
          <h3>Our History</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>2008 CF PharmTech was founded under Wuxi "530”Sponsorship Program</li>
            <li>2009 Received Jiangsu Provincial Innovation Award, and Science and Technology Leader Team Award</li>
            <li>2010 Secured a A-series capital investment, signed strategic partnership deal with Beijing SL Pharmaceutical</li>
            <li>2011 Wholly-owned subsidiary-Jiangsu CF PharmTech was set up in Wuxi; Filed 5 patents in China</li>
            <li>2011 Wholly-owned subsidiary---Jiangsu CF PharmTech was set up in Wuxi; Filed 5 patents in China</li>
            <li>2010 Signed strategic partnership deal with Beijing SL Pharmaceutical; The team was honored by China National “1000 Elite” program</li>
            <li>2013 Secured a B-series capital investment, startup Suzhou CF PharmTech</li>
            <li>2014 Completed the construction of Suzhou CF PharmTech</li>
            <li>2015 Secured a C-series capital investment, established the nasal spray and DPI production line</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content-card">
      <div class="card-img-area">
        <img class="card-img" src="<%= asset_path 'about-us-4.png' %>" alt="">
      </div>
      <div class="card-text-area">
        <div class="card-text">
          <h3>Plants and Capacities</h3>
          <p>CF has state-of-the-art manufacturing facilities in the city of Suzhou. Currently, it has four dedicated R&D teams and manufacturing lines: MDI, nasal spray, nebulizer, and DPI.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content-card">
      <div class="card-text-area">
        <div class="card-text">
          <h3>Our Logo</h3>
          <p>CF’s identity represents its commitment to provide safe and high-quality medicine to help patients achieve effective management care for their chronic respiratory diseases.</p>
          <p>The name CF comes from an old Chinese Poem, “Chang Feng Po Lang”, meaning hope and renewal.</p>
          <p>The logo incorporates the company name “CF”. It is an abstract image of the respiratory tract, illustrating the company’s focus on the respiratory area. The hexagon represents rationality, science, and professionalism and as a symbol of chemistry, represents the pharmaceutical industry. Blue is for reliability and tranquility and the “F” is a symbol of a sailboat which shows exploration, innovation, and discovery. </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-img-area">
        <img class="card-img" src="<%= asset_path 'about-us-5.jpg' %>" alt="">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
